are living together

293
00:21:11,433 --> 00:21:13,667
in this proto-city.

294
00:21:14,300 --> 00:21:16,800
The city is such a new idea,

295
00:21:16,934 --> 00:21:19,266
they haven't
invented the street yet,

296
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:21,066
or the window.

297
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:23,900
So the only way you can get
into your apartment is to walk

298
00:21:24,033 --> 00:21:26,934
along the rooftops till
you arrive at the opening

299
00:21:27,066 --> 00:21:28,567
to your dwelling.

300
00:21:30,033 --> 00:21:32,967
Çatalhöyük lacked something
much more significant than

301
00:21:33,100 --> 00:21:36,233
streets and windows.

302
00:21:36,867 --> 00:21:40,066
There is no palace here.

303
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:42,767
The bitter price that the
