314
00:22:20,834 --> 00:22:23,333
But, man, it was
anything but drab.

315
00:22:23,467 --> 00:22:26,233
Come on. I'll show you.

316
00:22:40,900 --> 00:22:44,300
This was a typical apartment
in one of the first cities,

317
00:22:45,300 --> 00:22:47,567
Çatalhöyük,
