00:23:18,533 --> 00:23:20,500
Every apartment had a
similar floor plan.

327
00:23:21,700 --> 00:23:26,633
Bedroom. Living room.
Kitchen.

328
00:23:29,700 --> 00:23:32,000
Plaster auroch head.

329
00:23:32,133 --> 00:23:35,734
The people of Çatalhöyük
had a passion for decorating.

