433
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:07,734
Then, as now, there were
those who were threatened

434
00:30:07,867 --> 00:30:09,834
by this view of God.

435
00:30:20,967 --> 00:30:23,500
Spinoza continued to
write and speak about his

436
00:30:23,633 --> 00:30:26,133
revolutionary view of God,

437
00:30:26,266 --> 00:30:29,100
always wearing the slashed
cape as a badge of honor.

438
00:30:31,300 --> 00:30:35,266
He died at 44, possibly from
inhaling particles of dust

439
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:37,333
during his years of
