470
00:32:50,200 --> 00:32:51,633
Literally.

471
00:32:51,767 --> 00:32:54,200
You just wait for
the wind to blow.

472
00:32:54,333 --> 00:32:56,467
If you get lucky,
some of your pollen will

473
00:32:56,600 --> 00:32:59,500
be carried away and land on
the sexual reproductive part

474
00:32:59,633 --> 00:33:02,066
of another plant.

475
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:04,600
The plants played this
hit-or-miss game of chance for

476
00:33:04,734 --> 00:33:06,967
a couple of
hundred million years,

477
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:10,834
until insects
